# column selection mode (really multicursor in vscode)
Option-Command + arrow to select column with keyboard
# Mouse behaviorBased on Selection>Switch to Cmd+Click for Multi-Cursor
                                   Switch to Alt-Click for Multi-Cursor
Shift + alt + mouse drag (from current cursor location) to select column
Shift _ alt + mouse click to mark end of column selection from current cursor position
- click outside selection to exit column mode
- sometimes buggy display but it works mostly (deselect/reselect to see highlights/insertion points correctly)
